set.seed(484)
N <- length(df$price)
s <- sample(N)
k <- round(0.7*N)
s_train <- s[1:k]
s_test <- s[-c(1:k)]

df_train <- df[s_train,]
df_test <- df[s_test,]
y_train <- df_train$price
X_train <- df_train %>% select(-price)
